import React, { useState } from 'react'; import api from './api'; const PredictionForm = () => { const [formData, setFormData] = useState({ // Đặc trưng số Age: 20, avg_enrolled: 5, avg_approved: 4, avg_grade: 12, avg_without_evaluations: 1, // Đặc trưng phân loại Marital_status: 1, Application_mode: '1', Application_order: '1', Course: '33', Daytime_evening_attendance: 'Daytime', Previous_qualification: '1', Mother_qualification: '1', Father_qualification: '1', Mother_occupation: '5', Father_occupation: '5', Displaced: 'Yes', Debtor: 'No', Tuition_fees_up_to_date: 'Yes', Gender: 'Male', Scholarship_holder: 'No' }); const [result, setResult] = useState(null); const [loading, setLoading] = useState(false); const handleInputChange = (event) => { const { name, value, type, checked } = event.target; // Xử lý giá trị dựa trên loại input const inputValue = type === 'checkbox' ? checked : type === 'number' ? parseFloat(value) : value; setFormData({ ...formData, [name]: inputValue, }); }; const handleSubmit = async (event) => { event.preventDefault(); setLoading(true); try { const response = await api.post('/predict/', formData); setResult(response.data); } catch (error) { console.error('Lỗi khi dự đoán:', error); alert('Có lỗi xảy ra khi dự đoán. Vui lòng thử lại.'); } finally { setLoading(false); } }; return (

Student Retention Prediction

Numeric Information

Categorical Information

{result && (

Prediction Result

Prediction: {result.prediction === 'Dropout' ? 'Likely to Drop Out' : 'Likely to Continue'}

Probability: {(result.probability * 100).toFixed(2)}%

)}
); }; export default PredictionForm;
